        <div class="centered">
            <div class="content">
                <p>We're an indie game developer based in London, and our flagship title is Zombies, Run!, a running game and audio adventure that melds GPS and accelerometer data with an epic story and fantastic gameplay. </p>
<p>With well over three million sales and downloads across iOS and Android, we get emails every day from people whose lives we’ve improved with our games - people who’ve lost weight, become healthier, and gained confidence. There’s nothing like knowing that your work is valued by millions and is doing good in the world.</p>
<h2>About Six to Start</h2>
<p>We create games and interactive experiences for smartphones, wearable devices, the web, and the real world. We've won a whole host of awards including SXSW Best of Show and Best Game, and before making Zombies, Run!, we worked on major projects for the BBC, Channel 4, Disney Imagineering, Microsoft, and the British Museum.</p>
<p>We're profitable, bootstrapped, and expanding rapidly. No need to worry about funding here.</p>
<h2>We have great benefits</h2>
<ul>
<li>We're a Mac shop, and you get the tech you need!</li>
<li>Personal budget for games, consoles, running gear, and more</li>
<li>Everyone has lunch together - for a full hour!</li>
<li>Opportunity to speak at conferences</li>
</ul>
